{"tid":2122903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海事處證1萬船員獲豁免檢疫 何栢良斥安排如「無掩雞籠」","createTime":"2020-07-24T09:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:22:57.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0469e3978093887d2772fa855fbf0cc0ca5130","tid":2122903,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"海事處回覆查詢時表示，自豁免強制檢疫安排生效以來，約有1萬多名船員獲豁免。海事處指經徵詢食物及衞生署局及衞生署，獲豁免的船員以及他們的船公司、代理必須遵守一系列特定條件和措施，包括所有在香港國際機場抵港以登船的船員，在離開出發地前的48小時內需接受核酸測試，並取得陰性的檢測結果及保證書。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/ON2NII265U2XPMAHSRG2XUFSDY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR23IG1myPNSFF7oAyRMf8SFbMxHgMyBEpx3lqC7UMtQ29LkvSwHiwTKPfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FON2NII265U2XPMAHSRG2XUFSDY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR23IG1myPNSFF7oAyRMf8SFbMxHgMyBEpx3lqC7UMtQ29LkvSwHiwTKPfE&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6D2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=4001e72d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FON2NII265U2XPMAHSRG2XUFSDY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR23IG1myPNSFF7oAyRMf8SFbMxHgMyBEpx3lqC7UMtQ29LkvSwHiwTKPfE&h=b1b4e2a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/ON2NII265U2XPMAHSRG2XUFSDY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR23IG1myPNSFF7oAyRMf8SFbMxHgMyBEpx3lqC7UMtQ29LkvSwHiwTKPfE</a>"},{"pid":"0eec836d58f520c81b9269a3cc642be94255395c","tid":2122903,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"a7d9057db628aa9c37c5f5c0932